{"text_id":172886,"tokens":["The"," opposite"," of"," a"," hedge"," is"," a"," risk","."," A"," hedge"," is"," a"," financial"," strategy"," that"," is"," used"," to"," reduce"," the"," risk"," of"," loss"," from"," price"," fluctuations"," in"," an"," asset","."," It"," involves"," taking"," a"," position"," in"," a"," financial"," instrument"," that"," is"," designed"," to"," offset"," any"," potential"," losses"," in"," another"," asset","."," For"," example",","," if"," you"," own"," a"," stock"," and"," you"," are"," worried"," about"," the"," price"," falling",","," you"," might"," buy"," a"," put"," option"," as"," a"," hedge","."," This"," gives"," you"," the"," right"," to"," sell"," the"," stock"," at"," a"," certain"," price",","," which"," can"," help"," to"," protect"," you"," against"," any"," potential"," losses"," if"," the"," stock"," price"," falls","."," In"," contrast",","," a"," risk"," is"," a"," potential"," for"," loss"," or"," the"," uncertainty"," of"," a"," positive"," outcome","."," If"," you"," do"," not"," use"," a"," hedge",","," you"," are"," taking"," a"," risk"," that"," the"," price"," of"," the"," asset"," will"," move"," in"," an"," unfavorable"," direction","."],"sub_source":"finance","model":"gpt-35","label":1}